        <h3 class="text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 mt-0">Child using another user account or Guest account</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-semibold">Solutions:</p>
        <ul class="pl-5 mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li class="mb-1">Disable Guest User: System Settings ‚Üí Users & Groups ‚Üí Turn off Guest User</li>
          <li class="mb-1">Password-protect all other accounts</li>
          <li class="mb-1">Check for unauthorized accounts regularly</li>
          <li class="mb-1">Use auto-login for child's account only</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-l-4 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-400 p-4 rounded">
        <h3 class="text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 mt-0">Screen Time settings not syncing across devices</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-semibold">Solutions:</p>
        <ul class="pl-5 mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li class="mb-1">Ensure all devices are signed into iCloud with same Apple ID</li>
          <li class="mb-1">Check internet connection</li>
          <li class="mb-1">Turn Screen Time off and on again on all devices</li>
          <li class="mb-1">Verify "Share Across Devices" is enabled</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-l-4 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-400 p-4 rounded">
        <h3 class="text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 mt-0">Legitimate educational sites being blocked</h3>
        <p class="mb-0 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"><strong>Solution:</strong> Add sites to "Always Allow" list in Content & Privacy ‚Üí Web Content. You can also temporarily grant access or adjust filtering level.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 border-l-4 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-400 p-4 rounded">
        <h3 class="text-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 mt-0">Forgot Screen Time passcode</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-semibold">Solutions:</p>
        <ul class="pl-5 mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li class="mb-1">Use Apple ID password to reset (if set up)</li>
          <li class="mb-1">May require contacting Apple Support</li>
          <li class="mb-1">Prevention: Store passcode securely</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

