          <li class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">Comprehensive controls</li>
          <li class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">Integrates with iOS/iPadOS Screen Time</li>
          <li class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">Easy to set up and manage</li>
