          <li class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">Safari-focused (third-party browsers harder to filter)</li>
          <li class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">Can be bypassed with admin access</li>
          <li class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">Web filtering is basic</li>
          <li class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">No social media monitoring</li>
